& [SLMSlice51GoldenFixtureSnapshots] is a work-ready slice for stable output fixtures
  + [slice_id] is SLM-51
  + [status] is verified_wsl
  + [effort] is M
  + [risk] is medium
  + [depends_on] is SLM-41, SLM-49, SLM-50
  + [scope] is store canonical compact outputs for selected fixtures and compare regressions
  + [acceptance_criteria] is snapshot diffs reveal graph, wobble, and primer changes
  + [proof_route] is CLI regression harness

  ! [CompletionEvidence] is the SLM-51 verification record
    @ [contract] is slm_project/specifications/contracts/SLM_Golden_Fixture_Snapshot_Contract.sop
    @ [implementation] is slm_project/tools/slm_golden_snapshot.py and slm_project/fixtures/golden/*.json
    @ [source_gate] passed
    @ [snapshot_check] passed
    @ [regression_harness] passed with golden snapshot stage
    @ [fixtures] are design_compiler, fish_swim, and time_flies
